{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because the smell of the soil is still in me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we grew things for, I think, the first two or three years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We used to get seeds with less and less.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my aunt lived with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My father couldn't get a job in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One time, I think-- I don't remember how they found out where his parents were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they went to the post office in the ghetto to send away a package from the meager food rations that we have.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was either the post office or the police station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were waiting in line a whole day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, you know, all the [NON-ENGLISH], favoritism, people that they knew got in first.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- and my father, being a revolutionary, couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So apparently he started yelling at the police with a few other people, and they beat them up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I remember-- he picked up a, a seat, was going to throw it at the police.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They beat them up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I remember, he came home all bloody here on his head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He, he was starting to lose his hair here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So it was all bloody because of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I think the police arrested him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I'm talking about the Jewish police in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I think he stayed one night in jail or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They let him out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they couldn't send away the package anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So there was no money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was not even any money to buy the meager rations that we got.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
